<div type="translation" resp="part:matr">
		
		<p n="1"> Fortune ! </p>
		<p n="1-6"> While the śaka year 1699 was ongoing, in the kollam year 955, which was a vilampi year, in the month of aṟpaci, on the 11th day, which is a Wednesday, at the time of a certain direction and star, under the sign of the tulā, on this auspicious day... </p>
			
		<p n="6-18"> in the land of the nine continents surrounding mount Meru, in the bhārata khaṇḍa, in the kumarikhaṇḍa which was separated, in the land of the Cēra, Cōḷas and Pāṇṭiyas, in the Pāṇṭiya region, ...
		</p>
	
	
